Sean McGowan , toy industry analyst 
at Needham & Co. Inc., discusses "The Toy Insider's Hot 20" and 
growth for  Mattel Inc. (MAT)  and  Hasbro Inc. (HAS)  McGowan talked with 
Bloomberg's Pimm Fox and Carol Massar on Bloomberg Radio's 
"Taking Stock" on September 25th. Matt Townsend, Bloomberg News 
consumer reporter, also took part in the discussion.   (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 09:23
 